      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Benefits:"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "\n- Inspired by "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "biological memory"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (human forgetting curves).\n- Works with "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "any vector store"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (Pinecone, Chroma, pgvector).\n- "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Simple to implement"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (exponential decay + relevance scoring)."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Trade-offs:"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "\n- "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Loss of rare data"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ": Old but important memories (e.g., \u201cUser had a critical bug 1 year ago\u201d) may be pruned.\n- "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Tuning complexity"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ": Need to adjust decay rate, weights, and budget for your use case.\n- "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Storage cost"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ": Still need to store metadata (last_accessed, access_count) for each memory."
          }
